      otherwise convey the Software to anyone outside the Owner's
      Employer.
  (c) The exception does NOT permit the Owner's Employer to remove,
      alter, or replace the Pharos branding, logos, copyright
      notices, or this license text.
  (d) The Owner's Employer is not granted any rights in the Pharos
